{
  "stem": "16503.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 14.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I was-- I had to go to a children's place, which was one room.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Like it was a building, girls' building, L1011, I think.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] we were in a-- like there was rooms and rooms.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "In each room, there was about 30 girls in bunks in that room.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And there would be a supervisor, a prisoner, same thing, only older one.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And she supervised that particular room.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I was very lucky.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We had a girl who must have been, oh, I don't know, 19, 20, something like that.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Her name was Irene, but we called her Uncle.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And she was the most delightful person there ever was.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And she made our life in the most terrible times the best she knew how.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "She lifted us into a-- you know, she was exceptional, exceptional person.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I today salute her, because she did return.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I saw her in Prague after the war.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I don't know what happened to her.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But to her, I salute, because she was an exceptional person.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she took us under her wing with the love and understanding completely.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
